Text: KMSnano activates via KMS (Key Management Service). It's good for 180 days (6 months) at a time. After 6 months rerun KMSnano to extend activation.
Is it possible that in 6 months from now the KMSnano program will be ineffective?

extracube

If Microsoft blocks the KMS host setup key that KMSnano uses it is very possible that KMSnano will be ineffective in 6 months!
